---
import { EXPERTISE_ITEMS } from "../../data";
---

<section id="methodology" class="space-y-12">
  <div class="text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto space-y-4">
    <span class="text-xs font-mono text-sky-400 uppercase tracking-widest block">03. Invariant Methodology</span>
    <h2 class="font-display font-medium text-3xl md:text-4xl text-slate-100 tracking-tight">Protecting Assets Through Pure Mathematical Hardness</h2>
    <p class="text-slate-400 text-xs md:text-sm font-sans">
      To guarantee that a smart contract cannot transition to an unsafe state, I mathematically model system variables as structural equations that must hold true before and after state mutation block events.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 pt-6">
    {EXPERTISE_ITEMS.map((item) => (
      <div key={item.id} class="bg-[#111624]/40 border border-[#1e293b]/50 rounded-xl p-6 hover:border-indigo-500/10 transition-all duration-300 relative group flex flex-col justify-between">
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-sky-500/10 border border-sky-400/20 flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-mono text-sky-400">
              {item.codeSymbol}
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-display font-medium text-slate-200 text-sm tracking-wide">{item.title}</h4>
              <p class="text-[9px] font-mono text-slate-500">{item.technicalLabel}</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 leading-relaxed font-sans">
            {item.description}
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-6 bg-[#090d16] p-4 rounded-lg border border-slate-800/60 font-mono text-xs text-indigo-300 select-all flex justify-between items-center group-hover:border-sky-500/10 transition-colors">
          <code class="text-[12px]">{item.equation}</code>
          <span class="text-[9px] text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wider font-semibold group-hover:text-sky-400/80 transition-colors">ASSERT</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    ))}
  </div>
</section>
